Package: SegmentR
Title: Segmentation in R Using Grounded SAM
Version: 0.1.0
Author: James Boyko [aut, cre]
Maintainer: James Boyko <jboyko@umich.edu>
Description: Tools for image segmentation using Grounded SAM (Segment Anything Model). It interfaces with  Python libraries to perform advanced image processing tasks and offers  R functions for easy integration in R workflows.
